contentrichtext.text: '''Zapadnaya''' is an [[impact crater]] in [[Ukraine]] (border of [[Vinnytsia Oblast]] and [[Zhytomyr Oblast]]). It is 3.2 km in diameter and the age is estimated to be 165 Â± 5 million years, placing it in the Middle [[Jurassic]].
